    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in spectacular, mint condition and presents exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, free of any chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with the leather upholstery still smelling fresh and showing no signs of wear or creasing. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been maintained to the highest standards with a full service history available. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle that drives as beautifully as it looks.",
