      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi everyone! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left for its next owner. I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with the maintenance, so it runs smooth and looks great on the road. It's the perfect reliable daily driver for someone who wants a quality car without the brand-new price tag. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 28900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera features the 3.6L flat-six M96 engine, delivering 325hp through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. To ensure long-term reliability, the IMS bearing has been addressed with a dual-row retrofit, alongside a fresh water pump and low-temp thermostat. The chassis retains its factory-spec PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management) for adaptive damping, paired with communicative hydraulic steering. Braking is handled by four-piston monobloc calipers over cross-drilled rotors. This example presents in strong driver condition with a documented service history, offering a mechanically sound platform for the purist seeking an analog 911 experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Regularly serviced. Clean title. Reliable daily driver.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior finish retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, accented by clean lines and well-preserved trim, with only the slightest evidence of highway travel in the form of minor stone chips on the front fascia. Step inside to a cabin that feels fresh and inviting; the premium upholstery is free of tears or stains, showing only light, natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All technological features\u2014including the high-fidelity audio system, dual-zone climate control, and touchscreen interface\u2014are in full working order. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced at regular intervals, with recent attention given to the braking system and a fresh oil service. The engine idles quietly and pulls strongly, while the transmission shifts with seamless precision. It sits on a set of high-quality tires with ample tread remaining, ensuring a smooth and confident ride for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies reliability and refined performance. This unit has undergone a comprehensive inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for mechanical integrity and driver comfort. Featuring a well-maintained interior and a robust powertrain, it offers an exceptional balance of longevity and sophistication. This is a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a high-caliber vehicle that remains road-ready and aesthetically impressive.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
