      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a mechanically sound example of the iconic S54-powered legend. The 3.2L high-revving straight-six features individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS, delivering a visceral 333 hp to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. Crucially, the rod bearings have been replaced and the rear subframe reinforced with plates to address known platform weaknesses. The cooling system has been refreshed with a high-flow water pump and aluminum radiator. While the exterior shows minor stone chips and patina expected of a driver\u2019s car, the chassis dynamics remain sharp with refreshed bushings and original dampers. A technically honest car for the purist who values performance over concours presentation.",
      "price": 31500.0,
